data.description: Immaculate better than new 2 Story, 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 Bath, 50 yr. tile roof. loft, Art niches, high ceilings, Spindled staircase, gorgeous bamboo wood flooring in entry, & living room. Kitchen is a Chefs delight w/ Abundant Granite counters (2014), Stainless steel appliances (2014), deep sink (2014), over-sized island, & convection oven (2014). Master suite boast vaulted ceilings, 2 walk-in closets, separate Granite vanities, Garden Tub, Granite in secondary & 1/2 bath. Surround sound in living room, Luxurious!
